Another object of the present invention is a process for the preparation of the co-crystal of the present invention, wherein said process comprises the following steps:
a) preparing a non-saturated solution of Ketoprofen in a solvent selected from 2-methyl -1- propanol and ethyl acetate;
b) mixing the non-saturated solution of Ketoprofen with solid lysine to provide an admixture.

