The DSC curve of Ketoprofen Lysine co-crystal Form 4 showed multiple endothermic peaks:
1st very broad endothermic peak (7.10J/g) onset 29.54° C., peak 70.81° C., endset 122,54° C.;
2nd endothermic peak (270.93 J/g) onset 152.18° C., peak 158,82° C., endset.
